A ENTENDER AS COISAS.

413
00:15:33,809 --> 00:15:35,310
TENHA UM BOM ALMOÇO.

414
00:15:39,064 --> 00:15:40,440
(CHORA)

415
00:15:40,524 --> 00:15:41,817
CLARE, ESPERE!

416
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:43,068
(CHORANDO)

417
00:15:44,361 --> 00:15:45,904
